<+><html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title>stories.TC_007_SCC</title>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\" media=\"all\">\r\n@import url( \"./style/jbehave-core.css\" );\r\n</style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"story\">\r\n<h1>&#65279;</h1>\r\n<div class=\"path\">stories/TC_007_SCC.story</div>\r\n<div class=\"scenario\">\r\n<h2>Scenario: TC_007_SCC_001 SCC  Create Internal Correspondence</h2>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">Given  I navigate to 'http://172.16.30.82:808/Diwan_Enduser/login.aspx'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I login as 'Sup-dew-1' with password 's'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Add Process Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Internal Correspondence Button SCC'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">When  Set 'Subject Field' value to 'random'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '&#1593; | &#1605;&#1583;&#1610;&#1585; / &#1593;&#1591;&#1608;&#1601;&#1577; &#1575;&#1604;&#1605;&#1583;&#1610;&#1585; &#1575;&#1604;&#1593;&#1575;&#1605;' from the 'General Manager Office Internal Correspondence SCC' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I select '1' from the 'File Name Internal Correspondence SCC' combo box</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  Set 'File Subject Internal Correspondence SCC' value to 'random'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Save Draft Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I click on 'Save Button'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I wait for '3' sec</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get value from 'General Manager Office Internal Correspondence SCC' and save it as 'GeneralManagerOfficeComboBoxValue'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get text from 'Subject Field' and save it as 'SubjectText'</div>\r\n<div class=\"step successful\">And  I get value from 'Internal Correspondence Get Serial Number SCC' and save it as 'InternalCorrespondenceSerialNumberValue'</div>\r\n<di